<!-- Freshness badge - GEO signal -->
<div style="text-align:center;margin-top:-8px;margin-bottom:16px;font-size:0.8rem;color:#64748b">
  <span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;padding:3px 14px;border-radius:20px;background:rgba(6,182,212,.08);border:1px solid rgba(6,182,212,.12)">
    <svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#06b6d4" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
    Updated: 2026-07-11
  </span>
</div>
<div class="ad-slot" ><ins class="adsbygoogle" style="display:block" data-ad-client="ca-pub-5998441792679372" data-ad-slot="XXXXXXX" data-ad-format="horizontal" data-full-width-responsive="true"></ins></div>
<div class="input-section">
<h2>墙体尺寸</h2>
<div class="row">
<div class="field"><label>墙长 (米)</label><input type="number" id="bcLen" value="5" min="0.01" step="0.01"></div>
<div class="field"><label>墙高 (米)</label><input type="number" id="bcHgt" value="3" min="0.01" step="0.01"></div>
<div class="field"><label>墙厚 (米)</label><select id="bcThick"><option value="0.12">12 cm (半砖墙)</option><option value="0.24" selected>24 cm (一砖墙)</option><option value="0.37">37 cm (一砖半墙)</option><option value="0.49">49 cm (两砖墙)</option></select></div>
</div>
<h2 style="margin-top:12px">砖块规格</h2>
<div class="row">
<div class="field"><label>砖型</label><select id="bcType"><option value="standard" selected>标准砖 (240×115×53mm)</option><option value="solid">实心砖 (240×115×53mm)</option><option value="hollow">空心砖 (390×190×190mm)</option><option value="perforated">多孔砖 (240×115×90mm)</option></select></div>
<div class="field"><label>灰缝厚度 (毫米)</label><select id="bcMortar"><option value="8">8 mm</option><option value="10" selected>10 mm (标准)</option><option value="12">12 mm</option></select></div>
</div>
<div class="btn-row"><button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="bcCalc()">计算砖块数量</button></div>
</div>
<div class="result-section show">
<h2>计算结果</h2>
<div id="bcResultArea">
<div class="bc-result"><div class="val" id="bcBrickCount">5,240 块</div><div class="lbl">所需砖块总数</div></div>
<div class="bc-tip">💡 建议额外购买 5% 作为损耗备用。砂浆用量为估算值，实际用量取决于施工技术。</div>
<div class="bc-detail">
<div class="item"><span class="val" id="bcWallVol">3.60</span><span class="lbl">墙体体积 (m³)</span></div>
<div class="item"><span class="val" id="bcBrickVol">2.31</span><span class="lbl">砖块体积 (m³)</span></div>
<div class="item"><span class="val" id="bcMortarVol">1.29</span><span class="lbl">砂浆体积 (m³)</span></div>
</div>
<div class="bc-detail">
<div class="item"><span class="val" id="bcPerM2">139</span><span class="lbl">每平方米 (块)</span></div>
<div class="item"><span class="val" id="bcBuyRec">5,502</span><span class="lbl">建议购买 (块)</span></div>
<div class="item"><span class="val" id="bcCostEst">——</span><span class="lbl">预估费用</span></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="info-section">
<h2>关于 砖块用量计算器</h2>
<p>免费在线砖块用量计算器，快速计算砌墙所需砖块数量。输入墙体尺寸（长高厚）和砖块规格，自动计算砖块数量、砂浆用量和总造价。支持标准砖、空心砖、多孔砖等多种砖型，可调节灰缝厚度（8-12mm）。内置常见砖块规格速选，显示砌体体积和砂浆量参考。适合房屋建造、围墙施工、庭院改造和工程预算。纯前端处理。</p>
</div>
